apt-notifier (1.1.4mcr120+7) mepis; urgency=low

  * Start a singleshot timer (50 msec.) after closing Synaptic or the 'View and 
    Upgrade' window. While the singleshot timer is running, don't process clicks
    to start Synaptic, or to open the 'View and Upgrade' window. This flushes out
    stored/errant clicks that occurred while Synaptic or the 'View and Upgrade'
    window were open.

